        "jsCode": "// 1. Kanjbdou l'objet li ja mn OpenAI (wakha ykoun wste array)\nlet data = $json[0] || $json; \n\n// 2. Kanjbdou l'text li fih l'markdown\nlet rawText = data.content[0].text;\n\n// 3. Kanms7ou l'balises ```json w ``` bach nb9aw ghir m3a l'JSON pur\nlet cleanJson = rawText.replace(/```json/gi, '').replace(/```/gi, '').trim();\n\n// 4. Kankhriwh l n8n m9ad\nreturn JSON.parse(cleanJson);"
